        </div>
        <h3>Ask Questions</h3>
        <p>Get your sailing and adventure questions answered by the community and learn from experienced sailors.</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="feature-card">
        <div class="feature-icon">
          <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
